* Introduction
- Simple lightweight resource planner and skills matrix for EU staff
** General
- DB of employees
- add new employees/people
- open to all, loo at anyone, no restrictions
- summary view, per office?
** Tabs
*** Overview/Summary/Dashboard
*** Projects/Hours/Time Planner
*** Skills Matrix
* Flow chart
#+BEGIN_SRC mermaid
Flowchart for secure employee data handling
    A[Load entries.csv] --> B[Filter entries for selected employee]
    B --> C[Employee Object: employee.entries_df]
    C --> D[User edits Confirmed, Tentative, Leave]
    D --> E[Press "Save All Entries"]
    E --> F[employee.save_entries()]
    F --> G[Load full entries.csv again]
    G --> H[Remove old entries for current employee]
    H --> I[Append new/updated entries for current employee]
    I --> J[Save full updated entries.csv]
#+END_SRC
